  "text": "Taken together, our data demonstrate the presence of small molecule melanoma-specific factor/s capable of promoting long-term EC survival under hypoxic conditions. This observation draws a parallel with a previous study where a small molecule fraction (< 3 kDa) of CM from malignant colon cancer cells was capable of preventing EC apoptosis. [CITATION_1] Elucidation and further characterization of the survival-specific molecule/s could assist in the development of new anti-angiogenic therapies to target the aggressive attributes of malignant melanoma.",
